      "comment": "ROUGH RINGO (4) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his sharp win the start prior, getting around this track over 400m in 24.39. Has the ability and expected to go close again. SHEER LUCY (6) followed a moderate fourth at this track two runs ago with another plain effort last time to finish fifth, beaten 6 lengths, in an A3 at this track over 400m (24.77). Well placed this class and looks a key runner based on best form. RAINS BONO (3) hit the ground running with a scorching early sectional but ran over late and missed the frame when a 4 length fifth (24.58) over 400m at this track. Can figure in the finish. BLACKBURNY STAR (2) warrants respect although new to this track.",
